y.navy.mil/FAQs/faq82-2.htm |archivedate=10 April 2014 }}</ref> }}\n{{shipwreck list end}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|20em}}\n\n{{shipevents|1945}}\n{{WWII shipwrecks}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=April 2012}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of shipwrecks by year|1945-03]]\n[[Category:Maritime incidents in March 1945| ]]\n", "name_user": "October1944", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200e8 March:Added name to ref", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_shipwrecks_in_March_1945"}
