/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Spain}}\n|[[Vox (political party)|Vox]]\n|style=\"background:{{Alliance of Conservatives and Reformists in Europe/meta/color}}\" |\n|[[European Conservatives and Reformists Party|ECR Party]]\n|{{Composition bar|4|59|hex={{European Conservatives and Reformists/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n|{{flag|Sweden}}\n|[[Sweden Democrats]]<br>''Sverigedemokraterna'' ''(SD)''\n|style=\"background:{{Alliance of Conservatives and Reformists in Europe/meta/color}}\" |\n|[[European Conservatives and Reformists Party|ECR Party]]\n|{{Composition bar|3|21|hex={{European Conservatives and Reformists/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n! {{EU}}\n! colspan=\"3\" |{{align|right|Total}}\n! {{Composition bar|61|705|hex={{European Conservatives and Reformists/meta/color}}}}\n|-\n!colspan=5 style=\"text-align:center;\" |<ref>{{cite web |title=Search {{!}} MEPs {{!}} European Parliament |url=https://www.europarl.europa.eu/meps/en/search/table |website=European Parliament |accessdate=9 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=About |url=https://ecrgroup.eu/about |website=ECR Group |accessdate=9 January 2020}}</ref>\n|}\n\n=== 8th European Parliament ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable mw-collapsible mw-collapsed\" style=\"font-size:90%\"\n! Country\n! National party\n! colspan=\"2\" |European party\n! data-sort-type=number | MEPs\n! Date joined\n|-\n| {{flag|Belgium}}\n| [[New Flemish Alliance]]<br>''Nieuw-Vlaamse Alliantie'' ''(N-VA)''\n|style=\"background:{{European Free Alliance/meta/color}}\" |\n|[[European Free Alliance|EFA]]\n| {{Composition bar 2|4|21|hex={{European Conservatives and Reformists/meta/color}}}}\n|{{dts|format=dmy|2014|June|18}}\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{flag|Bulgaria}}\n| [[IMRO \u2013 Bulgarian National Movement|Bulgarian National Movement]]<br>''\u0412\u041c\u0420\u041e \u2013 \u0411\u044a\u043b\u0433\u0430\u0440\u0441\u043a\u043e \u041d\u0430\u0446\u0438\u043e\u043d\u0430\u043b\u043d\u043e \u0414\u0432\u0438\u0436\u0435\u043d\u0438\u0435'' ''(IMRO-BNM)''\n|style=\"bac